msgid ""
"PlasmaTube allows you to watch YouTube videos on your phone or desktop using "
"a elegant user interface integrated with the rest of Plasma."
msgstr ""
"PlasmaTube-k zure telefonoan edo mahaigainean YouTube-ko bideoak ikusteko "
"aukera eskaintzen dizu, Plasmarekin bateratutako interfaze dotore bat "
"erabiliz."
